	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a level 28 druid and I have started to organise my spells, with another 20 spells to come from level 29 it does get clogged up.<br><br>Well I just organise them on type.<br><br>i.e. Nukes and DoT's, Travels spells, Animal spells etc etc.<br><br>I also keep the first 4 pages (20 spells) for the most used spells so they are easy to get when you need them.<br>&nbsp;<br>Coooooooo!!!!!!!</td></tr>
