	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a level 16 halfling druid, and was wondering what are some good strategies for leveling and getting money.&nbsp;&nbsp;I am currently bound in RV, and wandering round the Karana plains, the Gorge, and RE.  Also, I was wonderin what is some decent armor / wep that are both good and feasible for my level.  One last thing is, what are the spells I should be using, and what should I be lookin forward to at 19?  I apreciate any replies.<br>&nbsp;<br>Akaiinu<br>18th Druid of Karana<br>Sullon Zek</td></tr>
