	   <tr><td colspan=2>The gypsy in NK doesn't give any faction while the vendor in Oasis is a dark elf and gives some good faction with the dark elf vendors, and both the inner and outer dark elf guards.<br><br>The reward seems the same, so if you have good enough faction, or can get someone to inv you I would opt for the dark elf route.<br><br>One other thing to note is that at the lvl I was doing these quests, I found South Oasis much more dangerous then NK.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
