	   <tr><td colspan=2>Do NOT put any of your points into intelligence. Intelligence is used by INT casters including: Necromancer, Wizard, Magician and Enchanter (also the hybrid Shadow Knight).<br><br>Druids are WIS casters, along with Clerics, Shamans (also hybrids Beastlords and Paladins).<br>&nbsp;<br>-- Ancarett, who lives at <a href="http://ancarett.com" target=_new>http://ancarett.com</a></td></tr>
