	   <tr><td colspan=2>The prices aren't there even for premium members - but the links section shows the Caster's Realm which has approximate prices for all the spells.<br><br><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spells.asp?Class=Druid" target=_new>http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/spells.asp?Class=Druid</a><br><br>Basically you are looking at 1 pp to buy all your first level spells, 7 pp to buy level 5 spells, 12-60 pp to buy level 9, and 65-101 pp to buy level 14.<br><br>SOW is only 5 pp but Levitate is 8 pp.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
