	   <tr><td colspan=2>I concur with Darkparable below - I put 25 into WIS (giving 115) and the last 5 into STR (giving 70) for greater carrying capacity, damage in melee and quicker advancement of offensive skills. Putting that 5 anywhere else (apart from INT) will probably bring you as much benefit as I got from it in STR.<br>&nbsp;<br>Kelanthor<br>Wood Elf Druid of the 41st Circle<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672</a></td></tr>
