	   <tr><td colspan=2>at your lvl NEVR go near the orc lift or cb.&nbsp;&nbsp;stick to around the newbie lift or hunt at abandoned druid rings.  kill bats bees and wolfs.  also make sure u always buff your self with skin like wolf.  if things start to get dicy simply run to the guards.  also, try to get your newbie spells as soon as possible as they will help a bunch (especially panic animal-helps a bunch with the wolves and bats).  once u get snare remember to snare the mob first thing so u can kite the mob.  hope this info helps and finds you well,<br>&nbsp;<br>Gileril Wolfang<br>Druid of the 52nd season<br>Tarew Marr Server<br>Member of Mithril Storm</td></tr>
